metadata.name: Changeling
metadata.description:
In folklore changelings are humanoid creatures believed to be fairies that enter our world and kidnap humans all while leaving one of their own behind to take the form/place of the stolen human.

Changelings can reshape & mold their physical appearance to mimic humans & blend into their environment. Changelings donâ€™t just take the form of humans, they often seek to immerse themselves in the lives of their victims.
